targets.query:
SELECT sum("v") FROM (
    SELECT last("value")-last("value")+1 as "v" 
    FROM "transferSize" WHERE (
        "project" =~ /^${project:regex}$/ AND 
        "group" =~ /^${group:regex}$/ AND 
        "testName" =~ /^${testName:regex}$/ AND 
        "page" =~ /^${page:regex}$/ AND 
        "category" =~ /^${category:regex}$/ AND 
        "browser" =~ /^${browser:regex}$/ AND 
        "summaryType" = 'pageSummary' AND 
        "origin" = 'pagexray'
    ) AND $timeFilter 
    GROUP BY "group", "page", "project", "testName", "category", "browser",
    time($__interval)
) 
WHERE $timeFilter 
GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(none)

SELECT sum("max") FROM (
    SELECT max("value") as "max" 
    FROM "transferSize" WHERE (
        "project" =~ /^${project:regex}$/ AND 
        "group" =~ /^${group:regex}$/ AND 
        "testName" =~ /^${testName:regex}$/ AND 
        "page" =~ /^${page:regex}$/ AND 
        "category" =~ /^${category:regex}$/ AND 
        "browser" =~ /^${browser:regex}$/ AND 
        "summaryType" = 'pageSummary' AND 
        "origin" = 'pagexray' AND 
        "contentType" =~ /^${contentType:regex}$/
    ) AND $timeFilter 
    GROUP BY "contentType", "group", "page", "project", "testName", "category", "browser", "party",
    time($__interval)
) 
WHERE $timeFilter 
GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(previous)

SELECT sum("r") AS "requests" FROM (
SELECT max("value") AS "r" FROM "requests" WHERE (
        "summaryType" = 'pageSummary' AND 
        "project" =~ /^${project:regex}$/ AND 
        "group" =~ /^${group:regex}$/ AND 
        "testName" =~ /^${testName:regex}$/ AND 
        "page" =~ /^${page:regex}$/ AND 
        "category" =~ /^${category:regex}$/ AND 
        "browser" =~ /^${browser:regex}$/ AND
       $timeFilter
) GROUP BY "project", "group", "testName", "page", "category", time($__interval) fill(none)
) WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(none)

SELECT sum("dom") FROM (
SELECT max("value") as "dom" FROM "domElements" WHERE (
        "summaryType" = 'pageSummary' AND 
        "project" =~ /^${project:regex}$/ AND 
        "group" =~ /^${group:regex}$/ AND 
        "testName" =~ /^${testName:regex}$/ AND 
        "page" =~ /^${page:regex}$/ AND 
        "category" =~ /^${category:regex}$/ AND 
        "browser" =~ /^${browser:regex}$/ AND
       $timeFilter
) GROUP BY "project", "group", "testName", "page", "category", time($__interval) fill(none)
) WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(none)
